title: Multi-Cooker | KitchenAid
description: Behold the amazingly versatile KitchenAid® Multi-Cooker. With over ten cooking methods and four step-by-step modes, you can sauté, steam and simmer your way to a different dish every meal. And you can cook with confidence knowing its even-heat technology delivers precise, consistent results. Discover what you can do with this powerful cooking vessel: http://www.kitchenaid.com/countertop-appliances/slow-cookers/.

transcripts: The new KitchenAid Multi-Cooker delivers amazing versatility and consistent culinary results. Over 10 cooking methods, including four step-by-step modes, simplify cooking using precise and consistent even heat technology. Saute or steam vegetables without additional cookware. Simmer a sauce to perfection one day. Then enjoy a perfectly seared, melt-in-your-mouth roast the next. Prepare soups, rice, and even yogurt with one button as your Multi-Cooker simplifies complex cooking sequences and temperatures for you. Discover how easy gourmet cooking can be with your KitchenAid Multi-Cooker.
